e:T6f2,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Fellow better than Todoist?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Fellow scores 7.0 overall while Todoist scores 8.0. Fellow is best for managers and meeting-heavy teams, while Todoist excels for individuals and freelancers."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Fellow or Todoist?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Fellow starts at Free and Todoist starts at Free. Fellow offers a free plan. Todoist offers a free plan. Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Fellow to Todoist?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Fellow and Todoist support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Fellow vs Todoist?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Fellow holds an overall rating of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10. Todoist has an overall rating of 8/10 and ease of use score of 9/10. Users praise Fellow for excellent meeting note templates and Todoist for best natural language task input."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Fellow or Todoist?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Todoist for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Fellow remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize excellent meeting note templates. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}5:[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$e"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"compare-header","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container","children":[["$","h1"